data.description: Beautifully maintained four-sided brick ranch situated on spacious lot near all Atlanta has to offer! Fully renovated in 2018 this home has hardwood floors throughout, kitchen with beautiful soft-close shaker cabinets, excellently renovated bathrooms, open floorplan, and sizeable closet space including custom built-ins. Partial basement offers tons of room for expansion, building equity, and customization. Home is move in ready with side entry garage and large walk-in laundry room offering tons of storage.With an easy drive to several public parks and paths, East Atlanta, Decatur, Hartsfield Jackson International Airport, and Downtown Atlanta you canGÇÖt find more home for the money.
